S.FORM: alang Mrmurak ga niya mki sku Sincik Keng atu Nahuy go, kwara sali buwan nya ga 43 buwan, 124 hi ku kwara s'uli tayan. s'uli tayan pinspngan Gyencumin ga 94% kyan ku 117 hi, binah ga, 'yat kahun sku pinspngan Gyencumin ga 6% kyan ku 7 hi nya. pinspung na linhuyan Gyencumin ga, Tayan 92%, Amis 2%, binah lihuyan s'uli 1%. maki qu ngasal bziran. rhzyal kki'an tay 'llaw na Mrmurak hya' ga llyung. tay 'zil na Mrmurak hya' ga rgyax. tay mkyahu' na Mrmurak hya' ga rgyax. tay mkraya' na Mrmurak hya' ga rgyax. tay mkyahu' na Mrmurak hya' ga Spwan. tay 'llaw na Mrmurak hya' ga Metapay. rekisi kayal kyokay ssquliq pinlpgan ppqbaqan pqwasan biru 'laqi' cikuy pqwasan biru 'laqi' mrkyas tuqi 'san basu kisya' glgan spyangan na pinbahu Ubuy qqmayh
